{"tid":640393,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【彈入失敗】瑞典教練：絕不帶伊巴踢世界盃","createTime":"2018-04-24T09:00:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-26T15:31:36.000Z","uid":20634,"like":41,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"450c689aa733b0a0ecfb7c87a77f00ab1167b996","tid":640393,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:00:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2018/04/24/a/a2e50626ebac507136c933c23668b7ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2Fa%2Fa2e50626ebac507136c933c23668b7ee.jpg&h=b0773a64&s={SIZE}\" />　　<br />\n<br />\n在洛杉磯銀河隊效力的伊巴謙莫域，近來多次公開表態他會踢今夏的世界盃，但讓伊巴謙莫域尷尬的是，他被瑞典教練公開打臉了。<br />\n<br />\n　　瑞典教練安達臣公開表示：「伊巴謙莫域之前表示，他2016年歐國盃後退出國家隊，如果一名球員對國家隊已經說了不，那他就不應該回來。我尊重伊巴謙莫域的決定，但世界盃只對那些對國家隊說是的人開放。他一直沒有給我打電話，但我能肯定的是，伊巴謙莫域肯定不會出現在世界盃瑞典國家隊大名單中。」<br />\n<br />\n　　此前一段時間，伊巴謙莫域多次表示踢不踢世界盃由他自己的意願。伊巴謙莫域表示：「如果我想參加世界盃，我就會在那裡，國際足協阻止不了我。國家隊也一樣，如果我想參加我就會踢。」隨後不久，伊巴謙莫域又發推寫道：「我參加世界盃的機會非常高（Skyhoga）。」並標上了俄羅斯世界盃的標籤。<br />\n<br />\n　　如今瑞典教練安達臣卻如此回應伊巴謙莫域，看起來這位瑞典神塔的世界盃夢真的要破碎了。值得一提的是，伊巴謙莫域近來已經從傷病走出，他已經開始為洛杉磯銀河隊出場，並有不錯發揮。"},{"pid":"0c2d39be0707557e6181b1adecd31e4302eed96d","tid":640393,"uid":23734,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"349469bf1a3f941152265052916e47bdbf35e5e4","tid":640393,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:22:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"017fa5ed2288bd0b1fed9d90b3d09b3ead6601c1","tid":640393,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:24:22.000Z","msg":"X性家奴"},{"pid":"db9ea02a95f4f69be111479cce7fe813e6142696","tid":640393,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:48:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06aa7a4d893ceb55cab6a12cc1cedf204c73fdbd","tid":640393,"uid":10089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:48:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfacc0a81da9cb5a3a655422775009f5ca2da362","tid":640393,"uid":11895,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:50:04.000Z","msg":"屌佢真係當自己大撚哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e306d7475b5b02b07bc14cf19acbc314dc0517c5","tid":640393,"uid":139883,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:59:53.000Z","msg":"係咪串緊美斯"},{"pid":"26a6a6f0515ffd3fe470edc16d11e3e106c75d73","tid":640393,"uid":27416,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T11:06:56.000Z","msg":"唉無左佢呢次wc 真係無咩意思"},{"pid":"ee5191740887cbc1d88193b7c6c8cc5f62ce1ed4","tid":640393,"uid":10089,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"26a6a6f0515ffd3fe470edc16d11e3e106c75d73","tid":640393,"uid":27416,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T11:06:56.000Z","msg":"唉無左佢呢次wc 真係無咩意思"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:31:03.000Z","msg":"咁你唔好睇"},{"pid":"f5a64048498dfd1cc6abef2bd1a3e78e8a0afda3","tid":640393,"uid":54025,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T13:36:19.000Z","msg":"出撚埋statement唔撚比佢入了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ecd88ee05ea9c1df916c254e7f460353705c95a","tid":640393,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e306d7475b5b02b07bc14cf19acbc314dc0517c5","tid":640393,"uid":139883,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:59:53.000Z","msg":"係咪串緊美斯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-